subject: College World Series
lead_paragraph: Jackie Vasquez hit a three-run homer after the slugger Kaitlin Cochran was hit with a pitch, leading Arizona State to a 3-1 victory against Alabama and its first trip to the Women’s College World Series finals, in Oklahoma City. The Sun Devils will face top-seeded Florida or No. 5 seed Texas A&M in the finals.
